cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CL

The paper discusses the personalization of information and how user profiling can help in achieving this. This involves information retrieval and maintaining separate user profiles, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses various techniques and applications, which can be related to Machine Learning (cs.LG), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Computation and Language (cs.CL).
